src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bace8488c6852bdd3c80de0dc112388723013671","tid":548111,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:42:22.000Z","msg":"球員來講 <br />\n絕大多數唔會講 XX隊唔去 <br />\n佢地絕大多數是搵 <br />\nBest offer Best 教練<br />\n大把球迷去死敵球會  好像rio去曼聯<br />\n上面有人講史達輸去哂利曼<br />\n<br />\n職業球員 去比較大球會<br />\n (四大聯賽 頭幾名)<br />\n生涯基本最多得10年多d<br />\n23，24左右被大隊看中 踢到過30<br />\n(麥巴比，美斯呢堆另計)<br />\n<br />\n去一隊唔岩的球隊 <br />\n就算唔岩 一般都唔會即放 <br />\n如果係一支球隊坐2，3年 <br />\n已經浪費左自己1/3足球黃金時間"},{"pid":"d94019d7c3a5ca7ab7ddd9a583f24fa79744cd69","tid":548111,"uid":9305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9ca16f759b840f676c113dda59fe206e45ecab8","tid":548111,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"波台衰妹隻狗叫costa又點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n指既係邊個costa<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"Costanza"},{"pid":"f5f7f088bbef4d459406b001787a20364d4569da","tid":548111,"uid":4308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:09:20.000Z","msg":"佢去蝗係因為佢老豆貧錢"},{"pid":"7c718303154a16d0e81197227543e5615a772383","tid":548111,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66d8444abf2cde3335894b3ece6ae6295b1aebc7","tid":548111,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:26:52.000Z","msg":"我愛犬叫Xavi_Alonso <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:22:36.000Z","msg":"你老母好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15be44e95dbf9490025d369adbe77211085d2342","tid":548111,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66d8444abf2cde333589